00:11:38,043 --> 00:11:40,083
open world RPG that goes on for a hundred hours,

259
00:11:40,783 --> 00:11:43,324
what's motivating the player, right?

260
00:11:43,424 --> 00:11:44,824
Why, what's keeping them going?

261
00:11:45,124 --> 00:11:46,024
What are they engaged with?

