00:39:08,536 --> 00:39:10,117
It's because you don't need anyone else to do it.

793
00:39:11,038 --> 00:39:13,821
It's interactive storytelling that only the writer

794
00:39:14,081 --> 00:39:14,721
has to deal with it.

795
00:39:15,862 --> 00:39:17,964
So it's really good for rapid prototyping of ideas.

796
00:39:18,805 --> 00:39:21,267
