00:40:26,877 --> 00:40:27,758
Here's what's gonna happen.

826
00:40:27,798 --> 00:40:29,059
Someone's gonna solve this problem.

827
00:40:29,099 --> 00:40:30,281
We're gonna get some really great

828
00:40:30,321 --> 00:40:31,502
industry standard software.

829
00:40:32,062 --> 00:40:34,304
And then a year later, six months later,

830
00:40:34,324 --> 00:40:35,866
the quality of storytelling in games

831
00:40:35,946 --> 00:40:37,227
is gonna make this quantum leap.

832
00:40:37,928 --> 00:40:40,891
and they're going to think it's because all the they hired better writers and it's not.

