00:41:18,325 --> 00:41:20,147
I'll try to give you a short answer.

847
00:41:22,657 --> 00:41:27,960
So I think one of the things that's really important

848
00:41:28,100 --> 00:41:29,500
about growing as a game writer

849
00:41:29,600 --> 00:41:31,701
is figuring out which hills to die on.

850
00:41:32,381 --> 00:41:34,282
